# SearchInput 搜索输入框

基于输入框的搜索组件，内置搜索图标，并在 Enter 时触发 `search` 事件。

如果你需要“像 Select 一样展开结果面板”的搜索框，推荐使用 `SearchSelect`。

## 基础用法

### SearchInput
:::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="SearchInputSearchInputDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <script setup lang="ts">
  import { ref } from 'vue'

  const value = ref('')
  const last = ref('')
  function onSearch(next: string) {
    last.value = next
  }
  </script>

  <template>
    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; width: 420px;">
      <TxSearchInput
        v-model="value"
        placeholder="Search anything"
        @search="onSearch"
      />

      <div style="color: var(--tx-text-color-secondary); font-size: 12px;">
        value: {{ value }}
      </div>
      <div style="color: var(--tx-text-color-secondary); font-size: 12px;">
        last search: {{ last }}
      </div>
    </div>
  </template>
---
:::

## 远程搜索

### SearchInput (remote)
:::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="SearchInputSearchInputRemoteDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <script setup lang="ts">
  import { ref } from 'vue'

  const value = ref('')
  const loading = ref(false)
  const hits = ref<string[]>([])
  const open = ref(false)

  async function onSearch(q: string) {
    const query = q.trim().toLowerCase()
    loading.value = true
    await new Promise(resolve => setTimeout(resolve, 200))
    hits.value = Array.from({ length: 12 })
      .map((_, i) => `Result ${i + 1}`)
      .filter(s => s.toLowerCase().includes(query))
    loading.value = false
    open.value = true
  }

  function onPick(h: string) {
    value.value = h
    open.value = false
  }
  </script>

  <template>
    <div style="width: 320px;">
      <TxPopover v-model="open" :offset="6" :close-on-click-outside="true" :reference-full-width="true">
        <template #reference>
          <TxSearchInput
            v-model="value"
            remote
            :search-debounce="250"
            placeholder="Type to remote-search"
            @focus="open = true"
            @search="onSearch"
          />
        </template>

        <TxCard variant="solid" background="glass" shadow="soft" :radius="18" :padding="10">
          <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;">
            <div style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--tx-text-color-secondary, #909399);">
              <span v-if="loading">Loading...</span>
              <span v-else>Hits: {{ hits.length }}</span>
            </div>

            <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; max-height: 220px; overflow: auto;">
              <button
                v-for="h in hits"
                :key="h"
                type="button"
                style="text-align: left; padding: 8px 10px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid transparent; background: transparent; cursor: pointer;"
                @click="onPick(h)"
              >
                {{ h }}
              </button>

              <div v-if="!loading && value.trim() && !hits.length" style="color: var(--tx-text-color-secondary, #909399); font-size: 12px; padding: 6px 2px;">
                No results
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </TxCard>
      </TxPopover>
    </div>
  </template>
---
:::

## 后台筛选工具栏

`TxSearchInput` 适合承载关键词输入；当筛选还需要“范围/类型”时，搭配 `TxSearchSelect` 和 `TxSearchEmpty` 可以形成完整的列表筛选路径。

:::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="ComponentsSearchFiltersDemo" code-lang="vue" title="后台筛选工具栏" description="已通过本地 Nexus 页面截图验证的搜索输入、筛选选择器与搜索空态组合。"}
---
code: |
  <script setup lang="ts">
  import { computed, ref } from 'vue'

  const query = ref('')
  const selectedScope = ref<string | number>('all')
  const scopeOptions = [
    { value: 'all', label: '全部' },
    { value: 'docs', label: '文档' },
    { value: 'tasks', label: '任务' },
  ]
  const records = ['插件发布流水', 'Tuffex 组件教程', '截图核验任务']
  const filteredRecords = computed(() => records.filter(item => item.includes(query.value)))
  </script>

  <template>
    <section class="grid gap-3">
      <TxSearchInput v-model="query" remote placeholder="搜索插件 / 文档 / 任务" />
      <TxSearchSelect v-model="selectedScope" :options="scopeOptions" placeholder="筛选范围" />
      <TxSearchEmpty v-if="!filteredRecords.length" description="换一个关键词或筛选范围。" />
    </section>
  </template>
---
:::

## API

### TxSearchInput Props

| 属性名 | 类型 | 默认值 | 说明 |
|------|------|---------|------|
| `modelValue` | `string` | `''` | 输入值（v-model） |
| `placeholder` | `string` | `'Search'` | 占位 |
| `disabled` | `boolean` | `false` | 禁用 |
| `clearable` | `boolean` | `true` | 可清空 |
| `remote` | `boolean` | `false` | 是否远程搜索（输入时触发 `search`） |
| `searchDebounce` | `number` | `200` | 远程搜索防抖（ms） |

### Events

| 事件名 | 参数 | 说明 |
|------|------|------|
| `update:modelValue` | `(v: string)` | v-model 更新 |
| `input` | `(v: string)` | 输入 |
| `focus` | `(e: FocusEvent)` | 聚焦 |
| `blur` | `(e: FocusEvent)` | 失焦 |
| `clear` | - | 清空 |
| `search` | `(v: string)` | Enter 或 remote 输入触发 |

### Expose

| 名称 | 类型 | 说明 |
|------|------|------|
| `focus()` | `() => void` | 聚焦 |
| `blur()` | `() => void` | 失焦 |
| `clear()` | `() => void` | 清空 |
| `setValue(v)` | `(v: string) => void` | 设置值 |
| `getValue()` | `() => string` | 获取值 |

## 审阅说明

- 源码：`packages/tuffex/packages/components/src/search-input/src/TxSearchInput.vue`
- 建议：仅需要关键词与回车触发时使用 `TxSearchInput`；需要结果面板或选项回填时优先使用 `TxSearchSelect`。
- 交互：`remote` 模式会在输入变化后按 `searchDebounce` 触发 `search`，Enter 会立即触发 `search`。
- 可访问性：不要只依赖 placeholder 表达业务语义；在表单或复杂工具栏中应提供外部标签、分组标题或上下文说明。
